<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>BrickRide Customs</title>
<style>
    *{ margin:0;
        padding:0;
        box-sizing:border-box;
        font-family:Arial, sans-serif;}

    body{background:#f5f5f5;color:#333;}

    header{background:#ffcc00;padding:20px;text-align:center;}

    header h1{font-size:3rem;}

    .hero{text-align:center;padding:80px 20px;
        background:linear-gradient(to right,#ffcc00,#ff9900);color:white;}

    .hero h2{
        font-size:2.5rem;
        margin-bottom:20px;
    }

    .hero p{
        font-size:1.2rem;
        max-width:700px;
        margin:auto;
    }

    .btn{
        display:inline-block;
        margin-top:25px;
        padding:15px 30px;
        background:white;
        color:#ff9900;
        text-decoration:none;
        border-radius:8px;
        font-weight:bold;
    }

    .section{
        padding:60px 20px;
        max-width:1100px;
        margin:auto;
    }

    .cards{
        display:grid;
        grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
        gap:20px;
        margin-top:30px;
    }

    .card{
        background:white;
        padding:25px;
        border-radius:10px;
        box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        text-align:center;
    }

    .upload-form{
        background:white;
        padding:30px;
        border-radius:10px;
        margin-top:20px;
    }

    input, textarea{
        width:100%;
        padding:12px;
        margin:10px 0;
        border:1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius:5px;
    }

    button{
        background:#ff9900;
        color:white;
        border:none;
        padding:12px 25px;
        border-radius:5px;
        cursor:pointer;
    }

    footer{
        text-align:center;
        padding:20px;
        background:#333;
        color:white;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>BrickRide Customs</h1>
    <p>Your Real Car. Built in Bricks.</p>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <h2>Turn Your Car Into a Custom Brick Model</h2>
    <p>
        Upload photos of your vehicle and our designers will create a custom
        brick-building set based on your exact car model, color, and modifications.
    </p>
    <a href="#order" class="btn">Start Your Build</a>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>📸 Upload Photos</h3>
            <p>Send photos of your vehicle from multiple angles.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>🧱 Custom Design</h3>
            <p>We create a digital brick model matching your car.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>🚗 Receive Your Set</h3>
            <p>Get building instructions and all required pieces.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="order">
    <h2>Request a Custom Build</h2>

    <div class="upload-form">
        <form>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" required>

            <input type="email" placeholder="Email Address" required>

            <input type="text" placeholder="Vehicle Year, Make & Model"
                   required>

            <input type="file" multiple>

            <textarea rows="5"
                placeholder="Tell us about modifications, custom wheels, decals, etc."></textarea>

            <button type="submit">Submit Request</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Why Choose BrickRide?</h2>
    <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>100% Custom</h3>
            <p>Every set is designed specifically for your vehicle.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Collector Quality</h3>
            <p>Perfect for enthusiasts, gifts, and car shows.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Detailed Instructions</h3>
            <p>Easy-to-follow building guide included with every set.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 BrickRide Customs | Build Your Dream Car in Bricks</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>

